high_descs: Turn to the left and walk over the the dresser to the right of the book shelf.
Pick up the pencil on the dresser.
Step to the left and look up to face the top of the book shelf.
Place the pencil in the cup on the center of the top of the book shelf.
Pick up the cup with a pencil in it on the top of the book shelf.
Turn right and walk forward to face the computer desk.
Place the cup with a pencil in it on the computer desk.

high_descs: Turn around and then turn right to locate the bookcase.
Pick up the pencil from on top of the small lower bookcase.
